#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.argmax"
msgstr "# triton.language.argmax"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:4
msgid "简介：在指定维度上返回最大值所在的下标"
msgstr "Introduction: Returns the index of the maximum value along the specified dimension."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.argmax(input, axis, tie_break_left=True, keep_dims=False)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 说明 |\n"
"| :---: | :---: | --- |\n"
"| `input` | `tensor` | 张量数据，左操作数 |\n"
"| `axis`   | `int` | 指定在哪个维度上进行规约 |\n"
"| `keep_dims` | `bool` | 保持规约轴规约后的维度 |\n"
"| `tie_break_left` | `bool` | 如果多个元素有相同的最大值，返回最左侧最大值的下标 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Description |\n"
"| :---: | :---: | --- |\n"
"| `input` | `tensor` | Tensor data, left operand |\n"
"| `axis`   | `int` | Specifies the dimension along which to reduce |\n"
"| `keep_dims` | `bool` | Whether to keep the reduced dimension |\n"
"| `tie_break_left` | `bool` | If multiple elements have the same maximum value, return the index of the leftmost maximum |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tl.tensor`：同`input`的shape的张量\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tl.tensor`: A tensor with the same shape as `input`.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 支持规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 Supported Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:18
msgid "#### 2.2.1 DataType 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.1 DataType Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:20
msgid ""
"|| uint8 | int8 | uint16 | int16 | uint32 | int32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | bf16 | bool/int1 |\n"
"|---| ------- | ------ | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----------- |\n"
"|GPU| √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ |\n"
"|Ascend A2A3系列| √ | √ | × | √ | × | √ | × | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ |\n"
msgstr ""
"|| uint8 | int8 | uint16 | int16 | uint32 | int32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | bf16 | bool/int1 |\n"
"|---| ------- | ------ | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----------- |\n"
"|GPU| √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ |\n"
"|Ascend A2A3 series| √ | √ | × | √ | × | √ | × | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:22
msgid "#### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:24
msgid ""
"|        | 支持维度范围         |\n"
"| -------- | ---------------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | 无限制 |\n"
"| Ascend | 无限制 |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | Supported Dimension Range |\n"
"| -------- | ---------------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | Unlimited |\n"
"| Ascend | Unlimited |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:26
msgid "结论：在 Shape 方面，GPU 与 Ascend 平台无差异。"
msgstr "Conclusion: In terms of Shape, there is no difference between GPU and Ascend platforms."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:28
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Restrictions"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:30
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "Relative community capability deficiency and inability to achieve"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:32
msgid "Ascend A3 对比 GPU 缺失uint16、uint32、uint64、fp64的支持"
msgstr "Ascend A3 lacks support for uint16, uint32, uint64, and fp64 compared to GPU."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:34
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:36
msgid "更多示例参考triton-ascend代码仓，ascend/examples/generalization_cases/test_argmax.py"
msgstr "For more examples, refer to the triton-ascend code repository, ascend/examples/generalization_cases/test_argmax.py."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:38
msgid ""
"```@triton.jit\n"
"def triton_argmax_1d(in_ptr0, out_ptr1, xnumel, XBLOCK: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    xoffset = tl.program_id(0) + tl.arange(0, XBLOCK)\n"
"    tmp0 = tl.load(in_ptr0 + xoffset, None)\n"
"    tmp4 = tl.argmax(tmp0, 0)\n"
"    tl.store(out_ptr1, tmp4, None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:40
msgid "## 3. 特殊取值情况"
msgstr "## 3. Special Value Cases"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/argmax.md:42
msgid "对于 tensor[nan,inf] 的情况，返回inf所在的下标"
msgstr "For the case of tensor[nan, inf], return the index where inf is located."

